  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Ooh la la, I didn't pay any attention, because they-- in those demonstrations and meetings, they were all kinds [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There's always somebody that I don't know from the peace movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then there started to be people, started to come, all within a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they handed leaflets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I stepped over to him, and asked what are leaflet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When I looked at, right with his big fat black prints, 'Most Were Dopes.' They're all these J.G.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Endicott.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the whole, whole, whole peace movement is just a front for the-- for the-- for the Moscow communist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then without, without any thinking, I just grabbed the leaflets in his arms, threw it in the, in the garbage can, that there was a garbage can right at the entrance to the, to the, to the hall.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And pardon my language, somehow I shook him, turned him around, and gave him a real kick in between the legs, as, as, as I was trained to do in my service.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so, and he almost fell on his nose, and some that had just heard his what you call them, and just whining and just walked out from the--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but then it came, came back to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took, took some months before somehow-- it's human nature.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and, and my-- my tragedies, I have always wake up early in the morning, you see, and start to begin thinking, without, without knowing or, or, or one thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, a picture came back to me, that this man that, that, that I really flattened out, well, I know this man from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly, my god, this goes, goes back to the wartime.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
